  "rationale": "The official MTA Q7 row binds one realized onset and route to a three-member routing package: a western reroute, discontinuation and replacement of the Sutter/Pitkin segment, and eastern shortening with replacement JFK Cargo service. Canonical members retain the source-level service_pattern family. The official Queens Bus Network Redesign project context separately supports route_redesign as the reviewed bundle analysis family. This decision does not atomize members, inherit scope from another route, or treat the aggregate bundle-container record as an atomic treatment.",
